longBusinessSummary: Wonderla Holidays Limited operates amusement parks and resorts in India. The company operates through Amusement Parks and Resort, and Others segments. It offers various land rides, water rides, and rides for kid. The company also operates a resort, which offer rooms, banquet halls, conference rooms, dining restaurants, heated pool, and recreation area under the Wonderla brand name. In addition, it sells merchandise, cooked food, packed foods, etc. Wonderla Holidays Limited was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
